{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2016}} {{Infobox officeholder |honorific-prefix = Nationalrat |name = Balthasar Glättli |honorific-suffix = |image = Balthasar Glättli - parlament.ch 3003 -crop-.jpg |imagesize = |alt = |caption = Balthasar Glättli in December 2015 |order = |office = |term_start = 2011 |term_end = |deputy = |governor = |predecessor = |successor = |constituency = |majority = |birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1972|02|12}} |birth_place = |birth_name = |party = [[Green Party of Switzerland]] |otherparty = |spouse = [[Min Li Marti]] |relations = |children = 1 |residence = [[Zürich-Höngg]],<ref name="balthasarglattli-lebenslauf">{{cite web|url=https://www.balthasar-glaettli.ch/about/lebenslauf/|publisher=balthasar-glaettli.ch|title=Lebenslauf Balthasar Glättli|language=German|date=|accessdate=2016-06-03}}</ref> Canton of Zürich, Switzerland |occupation = politician |profession = sociologist and web designer |cabinet = |committees = |nationality = Swiss |alma mater = [[University of Zurich]] |signature = |signature_alt = |website = {{URL|balthasar-glaettli.ch}} {{de icon}} |footnotes = }}
'''Balthasar Glättli''' (born 12 February 1972) is a Swiss politician of the [[Green Party of Switzerland]].
== Political career == [[File:GrueneFraktionSchweiz2015.JPG|thumb|left|Balthasar Glättli, and among other GPS politicians, [[Regula Rytz]] and [[Sibel Arslan]] in November 2015]] Glättli joined the [[Green Party of Switzerland]] in 1991 and was elected as board member of the cantonal section in Zürich. Between 1998 and 2011 he represented [[Zürich-Seefeld]] in the parliament of the city of Zürich.<ref name="gemeinderatzuerich-20161107">{{cite web|url=http://www.gemeinderat-zuerich.ch/Mitglieder/Detailansicht-Mitglied?mid=9a64062b-516b-427b-81f8-e5506fb13e54|title=Profil Balthasar Glättli im Gemeinderat Zürich|author=Gemeinderat Zürich|language=German|date=2016-11-07|accessdate=2016-11-07}}</ref> He was elected to the [[National Council (Switzerland)|National Council]] in the [[Swiss federal election, 2011|Swiss federal election]] in October 2011, and re-elected in October 2015. Since December 2013, he is President of the Green parliamentarian Group<ref name="greengroup-20180621">{{cite web |url= https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/groups/green-group |title=Green Group |author=parlament.ch |language=en |accessdate=2018-06-21}}</ref>. From 2004 to 2008 Glättli was co-president of the cantonal GPS party,<ref name="balthasarglattli-lebenslauf"/> in co-operation with [[Marlies Bänziger]].
== Mandatory work == Glättli presides the ''Mieterverband Deutschschweiz'', the Swiss German section of the union of tenants, and is vice-president of the Swiss national [[Mieterverband]].<ref name="10vor10-20160603">{{cite web|url=http://www.srf.ch/sendungen/10vor10/fifa-bundesgericht-als-mieterfreund-em-taktik|title=FIFA, Bundesgericht als Mieterfreund, EM-Taktik |publisher=[[10vor10]]|author=|language=German|date=2016-06-03|accessdate=2016-06-03}}</ref> He is member of various NGO's like [[Erklärung von Bern]], [[Amnesty International Switzerland]] and [[Greenpeace Switzerland]].
== Personal life == Balthasar Glättli graduated [[Maturität]] at the gymnasium in Wetzikon in 1991, and studied philosophy, linguistics and German literature at the University of Zurich. Glättli provides a web design and consulting company,<ref name="politbuero-20161107">{{cite web|url=http://www.politbuero-kampagnen.ch|title=Politbüro Kampagnen & Webdesign|accessdate=2016-11-07}}</ref> is married to the Swiss politician [[Min Li Marti]]. They live with their daughter in [[Zürich-Wipkingen]].<ref name="balthasarglattli-lebenslauf"/><ref name="tagi-20151020">{{cite news|last1=Hohler|first1=Stefan|title=Ein Polit-Ehepaar im Nationalrat|url=https://www.tagesanzeiger.ch/wahlen/standard/ein-rotgruenes-nationalratspaar/story/18423738|accessdate=2017-10-28|work=[[Tages Anzeiger]]|date=2015-10-20}}</ref><ref name="tagi-2018-01-27">{{cite news|title=Nationalräte Marti und Glättli sind jetzt Eltern|url=https://www.tagesanzeiger.ch/panorama/vermischtes/nationalraete-marti-und-glaettli-sind-jetzt-eltern/story/15221958|accessdate=2018-01-27|work=[[Tages Anzeiger]]|date=2018-01-27}}</ref>
