A=Black Mike, B=Pontus Dammert, C=Markku Fagerlund, D=Pekka Helin, E=Raila Kinnunen, F=Kristina Klockars, G=Jari-Pekka Koikkalainen, H=Tero Liete, I=Kaisu Liuhala, J=Erkki Melakoski, K=Raija Sarmanto
==At Eurovision== Kuivalainen performed nineteenth on the night of the contest, following [[Denmark]] and preceding [[Portugal]]. Before performing in Bergen, one line of the song was changed, and the title "Päivä kahden ihmisen" ("Day of two people") was changed to "Never the End." At the close of the voting it had received 22 points, placing 15th in a field of 20 competing countries.
