The '''MT ''Bonsu''''' is a 16,000 tonne oil storage vessel that operates off the coast of [[Ghana]] in the [[Saltpond Oil Field]].<ref name=CONSOR>{{cite web|title=SALTPOND FIELD|url=http://ghanaoilwatch.org/images/blocks/saltpondfield_sopcl.pdf|publisher=www.ghanaoilwatch.org|accessdate=15 June 2011}}</ref> It was commissioned for operations in the field in 2008.<ref name=CONSOR/>

