{{Infobox Union |name= National Centre of Trade Unions of Turkmenistan |country= [[Turkmenistan]] |affiliation= |members= 1.3 million (claimed) |full_name= National Centre of Trade Unions of Turkmenistan |native_name= |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= |people= [[Rejepbai Arazov]], chairman |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''National Centre of Trade Unions of Turkmenistan''' is the sole [[trade union]] centre in [[Turkmenistan]]. It is a continuation of the [[Soviet Union|Soviet]] model of trade union. It claims a membership of 1.3 million.
